    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Indexing PDF for OSINT and pentesting]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.alejandronolla.com/2013/03/23/indexing-pdf-for-osint-and-pentesting/"/>
    <updated>2013-03-23T10:26:00+01:00</updated>
